About the Series:
(You don't choose the spirits. They choose you.)
The main characters of the series are the psychic, Alison Mundy (played by Lesley Sharp) and the academic 
who becomes involved with her due to his skeptical interest in the paranormal, 
Dr Robert Bridge (Andrew Lincoln). 
Set in Bristol, each of the six 45 minute episodes of the first series sees Alison become involved in the 
appearance of a spirit and attempting to discover why it has come back to haunt the living. 
Robert becomes involved in the first episode, when Alison first moves to Bristol and her activities 
inadvertently result in the suicide of one of his students.
